[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    173[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m [38;2;191;97;106mThe six-stage architecture (ingest and normalize, blocking and candidate generation, score, route by threshold, persist, schedule re-verification) is the right shape for a matching-against-authoritative-registry workload. The dual-pipeline pattern (Glue + Splink for monthly batch refresh; Lambda + OpenSearch for real-time onboarding) is the correct workload split, mirroring the 5.1 pattern with the registry-anchored deviation that the Lambda path now does one-sided lookup against an external authoritative source rather than pairwise comparison across the institution's own database.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    174[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The five-blocking-pass starting set is well-chosen and correctly ordered by information value. Pass 1 ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mlicense_number + license_state[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) is the highest-information lookup and "often returns a single candidate" with the candidate "almost always the right answer." Pass 2 ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mlast_name_metaphone + first_initial + state[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) catches records without a license-number field. Pass 3 ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mlast_name_metaphone + primary_taxonomy + state[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) is useful for spelling variations. Passes 4-5 ([38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mzip + last_name_initial[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m, [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mphone_last_4 + last_name_initial[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) round out the recall-vs-cost trade with the explicit framing that the phone pass is "low yield" and "useful as a tiebreaker."[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    175[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The hard-filter-before-scoring pattern (deactivation, type mismatch, license-state mismatch) is the correct order. The "deactivated NPIs only match if the internal record is also marked inactive" framing handles the edge case explicitly. The "Type 1 vs Type 2 type-mismatch fail" filter prevents the chapter-canonical "individual provider matched to billing entity" confusion.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    176[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The drift-snapshot pattern is the recipe's single most important architectural primitive and is correctly architected. Capture the registry fields most likely to change (practice address, primary taxonomy, all taxonomies, deactivation status, last update date) at attachment time; compare current registry values to the snapshot at each re-verification; emit drift events for differences. The "drift detection is the difference between a matcher that keeps the directory accurate and a matcher that produces a static snapshot that decays" framing in the Honest Take is the recipe's strongest single architectural claim.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    177[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The margin requirement on routing (top-score minus runner-up-score must exceed [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mMIN_MARGIN[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m) catches the "multiple Sarah Patels in the state" confounder that pure absolute thresholds miss. The "9.5 with a runner-up of 9.3 is suspicious" example is operationally precise.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    178[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The DynamoDB schema is well-designed for the access patterns: [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mprovider-npi-assignment[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m keyed on [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140minternal_provider_id[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m for resolved-identity lookups; [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mverification-schedule[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m keyed on [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140m(verification_due_date, internal_provider_id)[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m for the daily verification job's date-range query; [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mprovider-review-queue[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m keyed on [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140m(queue_id, candidate_pair_id)[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m for queue-by-area assignment. On-demand capacity choice handles the bursty batch-refresh-day-vs-quiet-day pattern.[K
[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    179[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The "centralize the matcher as a shared service with a single source of truth" framing in the Honest Take is the recipe's most operationally pointed framing and the correct architectural posture. The "credentialing care for compliance, network management for directory, claims for validation, network adequacy for reports - each builds their own version - matches drift" failure mode is precisely diagnosed.[K
