[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     66[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     67[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Structured logging. In production, ship JSON-formatted records
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     68[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # to CloudWatch Logs Insights. The medical-interpretation pipeline
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     69[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # operates on heavily PHI-bearing and biometric-bearing data:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     70[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # the audio is PHI and biometric, the source-language transcripts
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     71[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # capture spontaneous patient speech that often contains PHI
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     72[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # beyond the clinical content, the target-language translations
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+     73[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # are the institution's clinical communication to (or from) the
