[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    266[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     "consent to this collection.")
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    267[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    268[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # Jurisdictions with biometric-data laws requiring specific
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    269[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # disclosure language. The list is approximate and changes
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    270[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # over time as state law evolves; production maintains this
