[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    514[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    515[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Stands in for Amazon Translate's TranslateText API with
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    516[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Custom Terminology applied. In production this is
