[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    553[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    554[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Stands in for Amazon Bedrock's InvokeModel for LLM-based
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    555[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     translation on hard content categories and for the
