[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    708[0m:[38;5;10m[49m class MockHumanInterpreterPool:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    709[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    710[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Stands in for the institutional human-interpreter pool
