[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    712[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     LanguageLine, Stratus, Globo). In production this is a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    713[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     real integration over the vendor's API with routing,
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    714[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     interpreter dispatch, audio transfer, and billing
