[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    735[0m:[38;5;10m[49m                               encounter_type, urgency):
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    736[0m:[38;5;10m[49m         session_id = f"interp-on-demand-{uuid.uuid4().hex[:10]}"
