[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    865[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # up in run_demo() with fixture data for the scenario.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    866[0m:[38;5;10m[49m transcribe_mock       = None
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    867[0m:[38;5;10m[49m translate_mock        = None
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    868[0m:[38;5;10m[49m bedrock_mock          = None
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    869[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    870[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    871[0m:[38;5;10m[49m # --- Patient demographics lookup ---
