[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2481[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2482[0m:[38;5;10m[49m The pipeline ties together as a top-level handler that simulates a single end-to-end medical-interpretation encounter flowing through the seven stages. In a Lambda-and-Step-Functions deployment, the session-setup stage runs in response to the encounter-initiation event from the contact center or the telehealth platform, the audio-routing stage runs in response to the audio-streaming event, and the per-utterance translation stages run as the streaming ASR emits finalized segments; the demo orchestrates them inline so you can see the full sequence.
