[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2493[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Drive a single medical-interpretation encounter end-to-
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2494[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     end. conversation_segments is a list of (speaker,
