[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2601[0m:[38;5;10m[49m ```python
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2602[0m:[38;5;10m[49m def run_demo():
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2603[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2604[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     Run a single end-to-end scenario that exercises the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2605[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     main paths through the medical-interpretation pipeline:
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2606[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2607[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       Elena (64-year-old Mexican Spanish speaker, outpatient
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2608[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       follow-up for hypertension) is in the clinic with her
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2609[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       bilingual son. The encounter is routine_clinical with
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2610[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       machine_with_human_standby posture. Most of the
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2611[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       conversation translates cleanly. One utterance involves
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2612[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       a dosing change ("take 25 mg twice a day") where a
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2613[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       number-mismatch is simulated to demonstrate the hard-
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2614[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       gate escalation. One utterance has low translation
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2615[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       confidence to demonstrate the confidence-based
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2616[0m:[38;5;10m[49m       escalation.
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2617[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     """
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2618[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     # pylint: disable=global-statement
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2619[0m:[38;5;10m[49m     global transcribe_mock, translate_mock, bedrock_mock
[0m[49m[38;5;10m+    2620[0m:[38;5;10m[49m 
